{
  "id": "adv_event_2409_02_01",
  "title": "プロローグ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんの提案で、星見プロからみんなに\n誕生日プレゼントとして慰安旅行を計画したんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Based on Hashimoto-san's suggestion‚ Hoshimi Pro planned\na recreational trip as a birthday present for everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.5045124054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "旅行先は俺の方で考えようと思っているけれど\nもし、希望があったら受け付けるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm thinking of deciding the destination myself‚\nbut if you have any requests‚ let me know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "endTime": 13.5917005539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "グループは誕生日が近い人達で組ませてもらったが……\n日頃の疲れを存分に癒して来てくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I grouped people whose birthdays are close together…\nSo‚ please relax and recover from your daily fatigue!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8,
      "endTime": 20.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
