      "text": "イベリコ豚とロースステーキ重……\nふわふわのたまごサンドに、シュウマイ弁当……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Iberico pork and roast steak box…\nFluffy egg sandwich and shumai bento…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9820516385,
      "endTime": 38.1743193425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
