      "text": "美味しそうな駅弁を諦めたのに\n高級料亭の予約が取れていなかったなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I gave up those delicious-looking station bentos‚ but\nthe high-class restaurant reservation wasn't even secured…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3820516385,
      "endTime": 45.3153850991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3820539273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
