      "text": "私、もうお腹ペコペコですわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm absolutely starving now~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3820539273,
      "endTime": 50.5357502736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7487208483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、すずちゃん。{user}さんが今\n別のお店に電話してくれてるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well well‚ Suzu-chan. {user}-san is\ncalling another restaurant right now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7487208483,
      "endTime": 57.8621668933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0487200854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんから慌てて電話がかかってきた時は\nどうなるかと思いましたが、なんとかなりそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Satomi-san called in a panic‚\nI wondered what would happen‚ but it seems to be working out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0487200854,
      "endTime": 65.4506473659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.6487200854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
