      "text": "ええ。京都出身の優が\n知り合いの料亭を紹介してくれて助かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Yu‚ who's from Kyoto‚\nhelped by introducing a restaurant she knows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6487200854,
      "endTime": 71.5181079982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.7153867521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんが紹介してくれた料亭だから\n凄く美味しいんだろうなあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's a restaurant Yu-chan recommended‚\nit must be really good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7153867521,
      "endTime": 77.2559706487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.4487144905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
