      "text": "あまり京料理らしくない食材ばかりですが……\nそこまで素晴らしい料亭なら待つほかありませんわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those ingredients don't seem very typical of Kyoto cuisine…\nbut if it's such a wonderful restaurant‚ we have no choice but to wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6153811572,
      "endTime": 89.8525035022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0487170337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
