      "text": "ええ。嵐山の紅葉が部屋から楽しめる\n百五十年続く人気の老舗旅館らしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Apparently‚ it's a popular traditional inn that's been running for 150 years‚\nwhere you can enjoy Arashiyama's autumn leaves from your room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7820457894,
      "endTime": 102.226762529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.4153791228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
