      "text": "ふふっ贅沢だよ、すずちゃん\n京都は、私とお姉ちゃんでリクエストしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ that's extravagant‚ Suzu-chan.\nMy sister and I requested Kyoto.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2820457894,
      "endTime": 122.23780178599999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_02_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。私は京都の寺社仏閣を見たくて……\n千紗は、京都のパワースポットに興味があるのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I wanted to see Kyoto's temples and shrines…\nChisa is interested in Kyoto's power spots‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4487088957,
      "endTime": 130.7783233443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.982042229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
